{"tid":842473,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"集體回憶: <<秋天的童話>>","createTime":"2018-09-30T10:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T13:57:14.000Z","uid":164163,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0345b9e8444fafa3ace8726cadef179abf4017fe","tid":842473,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/181050_9561257bdd8100988437d670fdd6e1e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F181050_9561257bdd8100988437d670fdd6e1e8.jpg&h=2a327bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">船頭同茶煲明明都對大家有好感 但最後命運都係令到佢哋分開</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我睇完之後嘅三個鐘都仲好心up 好down</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">劇情真係無得彈 男人睇到都覺得好撚浪漫</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/181355_3a7f658c2a7e0b6df61e7289da855ede.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F181355_3a7f658c2a7e0b6df61e7289da855ede.jpg&h=026dd2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">睇完呢套有啲憎陳百強 覺得佢個角色好撚賤 周圍玩女人 仲要傷害我嘅茶煲 最後仲想食回頭草 好彩茶煲都唔再理佢 抵撚死</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/183505_f8ed3205d924aa83036ce7c81c31b3a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F183505_f8ed3205d924aa83036ce7c81c31b3a0.jpg&h=9f363f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實呢一幕嘅出現 只能怪船頭 如果嗰晚佢唔係毒撚心作崇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  已經一早食咗茶煲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/182422_d913df31856065d32ebd5512d5335bfd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F182422_d913df31856065d32ebd5512d5335bfd.png&h=571faa7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/181606_d8d697946ac77b3c638c3bcc005f5579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F181606_d8d697946ac77b3c638c3bcc005f5579.jpg&h=d49521be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/183039_a50515d4e1e634f176974a5c794288a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F183039_a50515d4e1e634f176974a5c794288a3.png&h=4cf20cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/183106_76538bbf6242053aad3ddd243d8c7e0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F183106_76538bbf6242053aad3ddd243d8c7e0c.png&h=4423c202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">命運始終唔可以將佢哋連埋一齊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/184558_ea65d67a953ec623f1e23d3a75e15a24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F184558_ea65d67a953ec623f1e23d3a75e15a24.jpg&h=3515d6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;Table for two?&quot;  <br />\n真係好想佢哋最後究竟有冇一齊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nBTW 張婉婷(導演)講過原本呢一幕係寫只不過船頭自己想像出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/184410_f1a5c3b8029b60f4a1460f7435631555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F184410_f1a5c3b8029b60f4a1460f7435631555.jpg&h=0469850b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/184436_b5c94a002e96bc25a412eff2b399a8fe.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F184436_b5c94a002e96bc25a412eff2b399a8fe.jpeg&h=2f4a140e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">曾經藏著的愛情 卻不敢承認</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a25ef6ba940b09fd2e9d5c3935c83691d648968","tid":842473,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a798f9b9576205772ee132336e76ec96f3792701","tid":842473,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db47d1382d500340d319974a5ae74b26cdf0da86","tid":842473,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"如果個結局佢地無重馮仲好啲，人就係咁，好唔完滿，珍憎過程好就"},{"pid":"00e879614a4846b990ee192f81c7f7ab36dedb16","tid":842473,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db47d1382d500340d319974a5ae74b26cdf0da86","tid":842473,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09